Package schedule.manager.service

Interface ScheduleManagerService

All Superinterfaces:
ScheduleExporter, ScheduleImporter
All Known Implementing Classes:
ScheduleManagerCSV, ScheduleManagerJSON
public interface ScheduleManagerService extends ScheduleExporter, ScheduleImporter
This interface represents a Schedule Manager Service that acts as a bridge between the ScheduleExporter and ScheduleImporter interfaces. It provides methods to export and import schedules.

This interface does not provide any additional methods apart from those defined in the ScheduleExporter and ScheduleImporter interfaces.

Implementations of this interface should provide functionality to handle exporting and importing of schedules to and from different formats or data sources.
